g.text: * It is a strategy to ensure that item hasn't changed before you update/delete it. (for ex. 2 people are performing operation at the same time)
* To implement this "Conditional Writes is used"
* Each item has an attribute that acts as a version number
* This will make sure that it is updated properly as we are checking version of the data so with 1st update version got updated to 2,
so no more requests for version 1 will be passed through.
